"""Generated playbook and PXE/Kickstart input helpers for aerolitctl.

The generate command is intentionally a safe planning/input layer:

* ``aerolitctl generate playbook`` writes AeroLIT-managed playbooks under the
  active ``collections-hub/ansible`` directory.
* ``aerolitctl generate kickstart`` writes PXE profile/template override inputs
  consumed later by the pxe-content generator.

It does not run Ansible, restart containers, render boot.ipxe, change firewall
rules, configure NFS, or apply system state.
"""

